Confirm Create MCM on Change Control Day

                  

                  

                  
Running MCMs on a change control day introduces risk and requires special approval.
We recommend rescheduling your MCM to a different time.
Are you sure you want to Create this CM on a Change Control Day?

                  

                  



                  

                  

                  

                  


                  


                  

                  


                  

                  

                  

                  

                  

                  

                  

                  


                  Warning: MCM tool is not intended to store or process sensitive information 
                  

                  

                  

                  
All data entered will be accessible to

all employees and contractors.


                  

                  
Please, check the
Data Classification Policy
or contact your respective security team with further questions.

                  
Alternatively, you can use
Secure SIM
to handle sensitive content.
